data.description: Awesome floor plan, move in ready, and sitting on an acre corner lot!  Main level includes soaring vaulted great room w/stone FP, elegant DR freshly painted, roomy designer kitchen, cozy keeping room w/2nd FP!  Split master/full bath with separate WiCs.  Quiet office space opposite generous laundry room, gorgeous hardwoods, heavy moldings, lighted ceiling fans & great storage including a big walk-in attic.  Bonus/4th BR has wet bar and powder room.  Screened porch & open patio w/outdoor FP overlooks nice level yard.  Side load 3 car garage with wood shelving & additional parking, recessed storage shed for lawn equipment too.  Minutes from shopping, dining, Lake Wylie!
